sourcesContent:
export const jobsData = [
    {
        id: 1,
        title: "Frontend Developer",
        company: "Tech Solutions Inc.",
        location: "Bangalore, India",
        postedDate: "2 days ago",
        description: "We are looking for a Frontend Developer with strong React skills. The ideal candidate will have experience in building responsive web applications and working with modern JavaScript frameworks.",
        requirements: ["React", "JavaScript", "HTML/CSS", "Redux"],
        jobType: "Full-time",
        experience: "0-2 years",
        salary: "₹6L - ₹10L per annum"
    },
    {
        id: 2,
        title: "Backend Developer",
        company: "Data Systems Ltd",
        location: "Hyderabad, India",
        postedDate: "1 week ago",
        description: "Join our backend development team to build scalable and efficient server-side applications. Experience with Node.js and databases is required.",
        requirements: ["Node.js", "Express", "MongoDB", "REST APIs"],
        jobType: "Full-time",
        experience: "0-2 years",
        salary: "₹5L - ₹9L per annum"
    },
    {
        id: 3,
        title: "Full Stack Developer",
        company: "Innovate Tech",
        location: "Pune, India",
        postedDate: "3 days ago",
        description: "We are seeking a Full Stack Developer who can work on both frontend and backend development. Knowledge of MERN stack is preferred.",
        requirements: ["MERN Stack", "JavaScript", "REST APIs", "Git"],
        jobType: "Full-time",
        experience: "0-2 years",
        salary: "₹7L - ₹12L per annum"
    },
    {
        id: 4,
        title: "Software Engineer - Java",
        company: "Enterprise Solutions",
        location: "Mumbai, India",
        postedDate: "5 days ago",
        description: "Looking for Java developers to work on enterprise-level applications. Strong understanding of Java and Spring framework required.",
        requirements: ["Java", "Spring Boot", "Hibernate", "SQL"],
        jobType: "Full-time",
        experience: "0-2 years",
        salary: "₹6L - ₹11L per annum"
    },
    {
        id: 5,
        title: "Python Developer",
        company: "AI Innovations",
        location: "Chennai, India",
        postedDate: "1 day ago",
        description: "Join our team to develop Python-based applications and work on exciting AI projects. Knowledge of Django or Flask is a plus.",
        requirements: ["Python", "Django/Flask", "REST APIs", "SQL"],
        jobType: "Full-time",
        experience: "0-2 years",
        salary: "₹5L - ₹9L per annum"
    },
    {
        id: 6,
        title: "Mobile App Developer",
        company: "AppCraft Solutions",
        location: "Delhi, India",
        postedDate: "4 days ago",
        description: "We are looking for a Mobile App Developer with experience in React Native or Flutter to build cross-platform mobile applications.",
        requirements: ["React Native/Flutter", "JavaScript/Dart", "Redux", "REST APIs"],
        jobType: "Full-time",
        experience: "0-2 years",
        salary: "₹6L - ₹10L per annum"
    },
    {
        id: 7,
        title: "DevOps Engineer",
        company: "CloudTech Solutions",
        location: "Bangalore, India",
        postedDate: "2 days ago",
        description: "Join our DevOps team to automate deployment processes and manage cloud infrastructure. Knowledge of Docker and Kubernetes is required.",
        requirements: ["Docker", "Kubernetes", "AWS/Azure", "CI/CD"],
        jobType: "Full-time",
        experience: "0-2 years",
        salary: "₹7L - ₹12L per annum"
    }
];
